description: The island's chair of the economic development committee says they "can't get the slots."
title: Flybe Guernsey-Heathrow link 'at risk' says economy chief
title_page: Flybe Guernsey-Heathrow link 'at risk' says economy chief - BBC News
maintext: Charles Parkinson explained: "We can't get the slots" and "it looks unlikely that the Heathrow service will be able to continue".
